{"tid":1236281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（未投請入）星期三或四 正反理據","createTime":"2019-06-17T11:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T11:44:34.000Z","uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a1a0743d64a0c8d473d8a0ce6ba827111c12314d","tid":1236281,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:36:38.000Z","msg":"星期三<br />\n+ 快D脫離膠著狀態<br />\n+ 政府、狗少D時間預備<br />\n＋民氣唔會散<br />\n&mdash; 其他同路人都可能少左時間預備<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n星期四<br />\n＋明日大嶼 星期五下午3點立法會財委會有東大嶼撥款 打到去星期五既話就名正言順<br />\n＋多D時間休息同做文宣<br />\n&mdash; 冇咁快，心急既人會等唔到<br />\n&mdash; 拖太耐民氣有可能散<br />\n<br />\n請各位細閲後再投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa1d26e0cb6f66bf952a458fb611d20862fad4d","tid":1236281,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:37:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe40181c2fe067c3d1546056a1239f1538fd4ef9","tid":1236281,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:39:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65e2b805536118364bd427806a4dcacd55f0890","tid":1236281,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:41:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07f4d2ed504bbef36b69370df9cb83bf506c39e3","tid":1236281,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:44:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}